{"tid":1991377,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"ESPRIT亞洲56店將全線結業","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:14:52.000Z","uid":34409,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d056adb7800d4d835d322b719a1dfda003e52dc8","tid":1991377,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"思捷環球（330）公佈，除了終止在中國大陸的業務外，思捷還決定關閉中國大陸以外在亞洲的所有56間零售店舖，尤其是新加坡、馬來西亞、台灣、香港及澳門。店舖關閉建議預期將於本財政年度末前完成。店舖關閉建議完成後，思捷將繼續中國的合資公司業務以及亞洲的批發業務和許可權業務，並專注於歐洲的核心市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200427/OUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200427%2FOUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4WztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=9761bd57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200427%2FOUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU%2F&h=fb809645\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200427/OUXAHMF6MZEN7KMSWAMFB2UFVU/</a>"},{"pid":"2e3ae8da44510117318e86b856424ff2d29ab8d9","tid":1991377,"uid":99962,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"H&amp;M will be the next"},{"pid":"bf6e7610dfd9552191666a47e1f5d36f049903bc","tid":1991377,"uid":130287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國企業撤資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒又近了"},{"pid":"e600396cafd202d13d4b5e267dd15b3293a3050c","tid":1991377,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf6e7610dfd9552191666a47e1f5d36f049903bc","tid":1991377,"uid":130287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad